ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b93454f3df4c3b097705e9c8e9ef538e3d226d","tid":2506634,"uid":37464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"681109d7243a35b5657e56c16a0dd3867eab2667","tid":2506634,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"I appreciate your effort but 至少最後嗰句有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n尾二句：各走各路如試煉 不知你或我更安然<br />\n<br />\n最後：言語自由今天看不見 只想像你走了 vs<br />\n原詞：無悔未曾可將你改變 都不被你污染<br />\n<br />\n唔講意境/呼唔呼應上句，其實自由本來就係看不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"夕爺最後一句我都鍾意，點出成份詞嘅主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實佢都無呼應到上一句<br />\n尾二同最尾係獨立成句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於自由，確實係主觀感受，理論上無法看見<br />\n但寫作上可以容許掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「那時其實嚐盡真正自由」- 《任我行》<br />\n<br />\n「同途在這星球　想出頭　打開了窗口<br />\n想觀看自由　走出了門口」 - 《同門》<br />\n<br />\n「風雨中抱緊自由」 - 《海闊天空》<br />\n<br />\n不過我同意自己收尾可以再靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa20056e9e4fe563de9763f859327a2f031185f","tid":2506634,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb62fc593320fbb89aefb7a8d994c93a5fd46f7","tid":2506634,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecc0303d9a02976293a13443137ecfa7179790e5","tid":2506634,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2d3fe51aa76a223d129ddbc0b844eb176538be","tid":2506634,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"推推推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img